  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TolE0210">
<l>aṉṉa veṉṉu muvamak kiḷaviyu</l>
<l>maṇmai cuṭṭiya viḷinilaik kiḷaviyuñ</l>
<l>ceymmaṉa veṉṉun toḻiliṟu collu</l>
<l>mēval kaṇṇiya viyaṅkōṭ kiḷaviyuñ</l>
<l>ceyta veṉṉum peyareñcu kiḷaviyuñ</l>
<l>ceyyiya veṉṉum viṉaiyeñcu kiḷaviyu</l>
<l>mamma veṉṉu muraipporuṭ kiḷaviyum</l>
<l>palavaṟ ṟiṟutip peyarkkoṭai yuḷappaṭa</l>
<l>vaṉṟi yaṉaittu miyalpeyaṉa moḻipa</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The verbal participle <foreign xml:lang="ta">cāva</foreign> may lose</l>
<l>its final <foreign xml:lang="ta">va.</foreign><note place="foot">E.g. <foreign xml:lang="ta">cāvakkutti &gt; cākkutti (Kalittokai 105.35)</foreign> ' wounded to die '.</note></l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
